    public class AddAll<SOURCE,TARGET>
extends Transform<SOURCE,TARGET,Boolean,Position.Readable<TARGET>>
    "Add all" transformation. Like Collection.addAll(Collection) result of an AddAll operation is intended to reflect whether a change was made to the target position.
